    "description": "Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Real Estate Agent for our Varanasi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates:\nSunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sunteck Realty Asia Pacific Associates!",
